content: Worked great the first day now it won't connect keeps saying "Connection Failed".
Smooth and seamless connection to my HMI on wifi. I can even make connections to HMI through the internet using a Tosibox VPN gateway.
Can't get it to connect to car wash equipment just as others reviewed. Can't get in touch with app designers to help. Do not waste your $30.00.
It crashes when i rotate the screen.
